Class NonpostedReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • adg.nonpostedreport.nonpostedreporter.NonpostedReporter

  • public class NonpostedReporter
extends java.lang.Object
    Takes in the two give excel files to parse into arrays. Then compares the arrays to find the inconsistent requisitions (the requisitions that are in one but not the other - the nonposted requisitions).

    Courtney Ripoll

    • Constructor Detail

      • NonpostedReporter

        public NonpostedReporter(java.lang.String fileName,
                         java.lang.String currentADGJobsFile,
                         java.lang.String myCurrentReqsFile,
                         java.lang.String filter)
        This method calls all the functionality of the program. It takes in two file names to receive the lists of requisitions to compare. It will get the list of current ADG requisitions and all current requisitions. Then these lists will be compared to generate a list of nonposted requisitions. These requisitions will be written to a new excel file and posted on the Desktop.
        Parameters:
        fileName - desired file name given by the user
        currentADGJobsFile - file name for the Excel Workbook of current ADG Requisitions
        myCurrentReqsFile - file name for the Excel Workbook of all current requisitions
        filter - if not null, filters the results by requested by
